    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Chamomilla recutita are anxiety and insomnia, for which the essential oil has been shown to have a sedative effect on the nervous system, reducing anxiety by regulating the body's GABA levels and promoting relaxation. Chamomilla recutita's anti-inflammatory properties also make it effective in reducing inflammation in the digestive tract, alleviating digestive issues such as gastroenteritis and nausea. Stress, headaches, and muscle spasms are alleviated by the plant's ability to relax smooth muscle and reduce muscle tension. Menstrual cramps, eczema, and skin irritations are also treated by the plant's anti-inflammatory and anti-allergic properties, which soothe and calm irritated skin. Additionally, allergies, restlessness, digestive disorders, gastroenteritis, sleep disorders, muscle pain, and restless leg syndrome are alleviated by the plant's ability to regulate the body's response to stress and promote relaxation.",
